| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2713 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f2ae383f-5ddd-58e9-b01a-f9f41e70fe20"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
